These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
City: boston, colone
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, dancing
The people have 2 different jobs:  lawyer, teacher
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the person traveling to colone is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| City   | colone    | boston |
| Hobby         | dancing | drawing    |
| Job     | lawyer     | teacher      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: june, december
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: azalea, daisy
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, librarian
1. the librarian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who growsazalea is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Birthday      | december  | june   |
| Flower   | daisy | azalea  |
| Job     | librarian   | writer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, iced-tea
There are 2 different favourite colors: red, blue
House: victorian, art-deco
1. the person drinking iced-tea is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes red is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate   | iced-tea  |
| Color   | blue | red  |
| House         | victorian   | art-deco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, skiing
There are 2 different nationalities: indian, indonesian
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bolivar
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the indonesian##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Sport          | soccer | skiing |
| Nationality   | indonesian   | indian   |
| Cigar     | bolivar       | pall-mall      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-5::.
