.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-6::.
2 different games are played: scrabble, snooker
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship
2 different pets are kept: dog, guinea-pig
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the owner of the dog is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Game         | scrabble    | snooker    |
| Transport   | ship     | quad-bike      |
| Pet         | dog | guinea-pig |

