.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, may
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: sunflower, marigold
House: cape-cod, townhouse
1. the townhouse house is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3
3. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Birthday    | may | april     |
| Flower     | marigold | sunflower |
| House   | townhouse | cape-cod    |

 #################################

 
