2. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| City           | boston     | marseilles |
| Hobby   | writing | dancing  |
| Pet     | frog      | goat |

