.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
House: cottage, victorian
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, roller
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk
1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
3. the cottage house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| House         | victorian | cottage |
| Transport   | van     | roller     |
| Beverage           | almond-milk          | mirinda     |

